---
description: Standard .gitignore template — read when creating or editing .gitignore files
globs: "**/.gitignore"
alwaysApply: false
---
# .gitignore Template

Always ignore:

```gitignore
# Environment
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# IDE
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo

# Dependencies
node_modules/
venv/
.venv/
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# Build artifacts
dist/
build/
*.egg-info/
.cache/

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Secrets (never commit)
*.pem
*.key
*credentials*
*secret*
```
